# The `DbgValueLocEntry` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

A single location or constant within a variable location description, with either a single entry (with an optional <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/diexpression">DIExpression</a>) used for a DBG&#95;VALUE, or a list of entries used for a DBG&#95;VALUE&#95;LIST. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

A single location or constant within a variable location description, with either a single entry (with an optional <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/diexpression">DIExpression</a>) used for a DBG&#95;VALUE, or a list of entries used for a DBG&#95;VALUE&#95;LIST.
